    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this absolute gem! It has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's in incredible shape\u2014no scratches, no weird smells, just pure perfection. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm only letting it go because I'm downsizing. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love it! \u2728",
