    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with zero imperfections, having been preserved exclusively in a climate-controlled environment. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in preservation: the leather remains supple and retains its original factory scent, with every electronic component, button, and switch functioning with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is indistinguishable from new, supported by a comprehensive binder of meticulous service records. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model. It is ready for a discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
