      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless inside and out! I've babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's practically perfect without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
