    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 power plant remains in peak mechanical health, benefiting from proactive rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. This example features a perfectly calibrated chassis with fresh OEM dampers and bushings, preserving the legendary 50/50 weight distribution balance. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of the analog driving era, free from any mechanical or cosmetic compromises. The factory-original finish remains flawless, and the interior retains its factory-fresh matte texture on all touchpoints.",
